and the best part is you can try it right now! 

Don’t let anyone tell you that doodling is bad; it is actually one of the best tools you can use to help you get ‘in the zone’ when you’re focused and able to remember more 🧠 

You want to keep your doodling in the happy equilibrium between not too distracting but not under-stimulating ✏️ 

